anything about it.

00:10:02.720 --> 00:10:06.080
Yes, they thought it was all a scam
until P&O phoned them back hours

00:10:06.080 --> 00:10:14.039
before the ship was due to board
confirming the cancellation.

00:10:14.919 --> 00:10:24.360
Did they explain why it was so late?

00:10:24.440 --> 00:10:31.799
They offered discount on another
cruise but many have said, not

00:10:31.799 --> 00:10:35.519
likely and there are also additional
costs like insurance and parking and

00:10:35.519 --> 00:10:40.799
time taken off work for dog care.
